v0.1.7
* Fixed formatting bug in Exchange Rates provider that resulted in no exchange rates (from least two reports)
* Fixed bug in Exchange Rates Provider that would crash the app (from at least three reports)
* Updated the two pane view to use the "middle" graphic
* Updated splash screen with bigger QRK logo and Beta text reminder to send crash reports.
* Updated footer graphics to display properly
* updated with more reliable nodes (though there is a 6 connection limitation still)

