v0.1.5
* Changed Block Explorer to qrk.blockr.io

v0.1.2
* fixed a send bug that would crash the app due to a BTC precision issue.
* Added native support for the Proof of Work Hash Function; may speed up syncing and use less power.

v0.1.1
* Sending coins using local currency inputs:  This should work better (before $100 was converted to 1.29 QRK instead of 1290 QRK).
* Exchange Rate information sometimes displayed only BTC with a 0.00 value.  This was resulting from a Cryptsy related error.  BTER has been added as a backup exchange for QRK price.
* Changed default units from mQRK to QRK
* Added URI scheme quarkcoin:
